{"id": "98895", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=98895", "title": "Azal's Staff", "text": "Azal's Staff is a &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt; in .\nAvailability.\nOn a corpse on a broken bridge in &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20Eleum%20Loyce\"&gt;Frozen Eleum Loyce&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nAzal's Staff is a staff of extremes. It lowers the player's spell uses by 75% rounding down, has very slow casting speed (only the &lt;a href=\"Chime%20of%20Screams\"&gt;Chime of Screams&lt;/a&gt; is slower), and is extremely fragile, exhausting it's mere 4 durability with just a few casts. However, it has an S &lt;a href=\"Parameter%20Bonus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; in both &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt;, allowing for a maximum increase of 540 for both elements in scaling damage and an effect that increases damage by 2.5%.\n&lt;a href=\"Bracing%20Knuckle%20Ring\"&gt;Bracing Knuckle Ring&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Repair%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Repair&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Repair%20Powder%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Repair Powder&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Clear%20Bluestone%20Ring\"&gt;Clear Bluestone Ring&lt;/a&gt;, can help to combat this staff's debilitating downsides, though unless the player has an use for having extreme scaling in \"both\" Magic and Dark, a specialized staff such as &lt;a href=\"Staff%20of%20Wisdom\"&gt;Staff of Wisdom&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Sunset%20Staff\"&gt;Sunset Staff&lt;/a&gt; will generally serve much better."}
