{"id": "131058", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=131058", "title": "Barbed Straight Sword (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Barbed Straight Sword is a &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;straight sword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20the%20Deep\"&gt;Cathedral of the Deep&lt;/a&gt;. Guaranteed drop from &lt;a href=\"Longfinger%20Kirk\"&gt;Longfinger Kirk&lt;/a&gt;, who invades as a &lt;a href=\"dark%20spirit\"&gt;dark spirit&lt;/a&gt; upon reaching the main open area located between the two &lt;a href=\"Giant%20Slave\"&gt;Giant Slave&lt;/a&gt;s.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Barbed Straight Sword shares the same &lt;a href=\"Moveset%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;moveset&lt;/a&gt; as the &lt;a href=\"Long%20Sword\"&gt;Long Sword&lt;/a&gt;, except each successful attack also causes &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;bleed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt;, which upon infliction, will take off a sizable portion of an enemy's &lt;a href=\"HP%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt is able to be buffed with both &lt;a href=\"Items%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;resins&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Spells%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;spells&lt;/a&gt;.\nAs a note, the strong attack whilst in &lt;a href=\"Stance%20%28Straight%20Sword%29\"&gt;Stance&lt;/a&gt; will cause notably more bleed build-up if the attack connects with the target.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with &lt;a href=\"Titanite%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Titanite&lt;/a&gt;."}
