{"id": "8054", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8054", "title": "Black Tights", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nBlack Tights are pieces in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". They are part of the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Set\"&gt;Black Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nFound in the Annex portion of the &lt;a href=\"Painted%20World%20of%20Ariamis\"&gt;Painted World of Ariamis&lt;/a&gt;, close to &lt;a href=\"Vow%20of%20Silence\"&gt;Vow of Silence&lt;/a&gt;. Can most easily be accessed after finding the &lt;a href=\"Annex%20Key\"&gt;Annex Key&lt;/a&gt;, although it is possible to reach it without the key.\nCharacteristics.\nWhile these tights appear stylish and offer good\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0resist, their defence levels are lacking and are upgraded with\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Twinkling%20Titanite\"&gt;Twinkling Titanite&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpgrades.\nRequires 200 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
{"id": "60771", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=60771", "title": "Black Witch's Staff", "text": "The Black Witch's Staff\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe Black Witch's Staff can be used to cast all &lt;a href=\"hexes\"&gt;hexes&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Miracles%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;miracles&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;sorceries&lt;/a&gt;. However, despite the fact that it deals &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage and scales with the player's Fire Bonus, it cannot be used to cast &lt;a href=\"Pyromancy%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;pyromancies&lt;/a&gt;.\nOne of the most versatile casting tools around; it is ideal for builds that regularly use sorceries, miracles and hexes together, as it removes the necessity of having a &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;chime&lt;/a&gt; equipped. Furthermore, it can be reinforced with standard Titanite, making it very easy to fully upgrade.\nMelee attacking with the staff, while having moderately low attack speed and short reach, deals impressive damage as it has damage values and scaling with all four elemental damage types.\nIt does suffer from poor stat scaling on &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage, making it inferior to most &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;sacred chimes&lt;/a&gt; in terms of using &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20Spear%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lightning Spear&lt;/a&gt; or similar abilities. It also cannot be &lt;a href=\"Infusion\"&gt;infused&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Boltstone\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt;, unlike chimes. This makes it excel with miracles that do not scale with lightning damage, such as &lt;a href=\"Heal%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Heal&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Great%20Magic%20Barrier%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Great Magic Barrier&lt;/a&gt;."}
