{"id": "131425", "revid": "1188343", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=131425", "title": "Blessed Gem", "text": "Blessed Gems are in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nUsage.\nGrants &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Parameter%20Bonus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; to any innate &lt;a href=\"Physical%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage, or increases any prior Faith scaling, but reduces &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt; scaling, along with reducing base damage considerably.\nWhen wielded, the player slowly regenerates health at a rate of 3 &lt;a href=\"Hit%20Points%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt; every 4 seconds, or 0.75 HP per second. Reinforcing it will reduce the tick interval by 0.25 seconds per upgrade level. At +10 reinforcement, a Blessed weapon will replenish 3 HP per 1.5 seconds, or 2 HP per second.\nWeapons with the Blessed infusion will deal 20% bonus damage to skeletal creatures (e.g., most foes within &lt;a href=\"Catacombs%20of%20Carthus\"&gt;Catacombs of Carthus&lt;/a&gt;). Killing an enemy with a blessed weapon also prevents them from reviving.\nIf infused onto a shield, its damage absorption will drop 5% across the board, and stability will be reduced to base value (e.g., will not increase with upgrades)."}
{"id": "133496", "revid": "51254358", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133496", "title": "Blessed Weapon", "text": "Blessed Weapon (\u6b66\u5668\u306e\u795d\u798f) is a &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nSold by &lt;a href=\"Irina%20of%20Carim\"&gt;Irina of Carim&lt;/a&gt; for 8,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; once she has been given the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Braille%20Divine%20Tome%20of%20Lothric\"&gt;Braille Divine Tome of Lothric&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nBuffs right-hand weapon, increasing &lt;a href=\"Physical%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt; damage by 7.5%, and also gradually restoring &lt;a href=\"HP%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt; for 45 seconds. The HP restored per second is 1 for every 50 &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; of the casting tool used.\nAdditionally, the weapon gains the same properties as a &lt;a href=\"Blessed%20Gem\"&gt;Blessed&lt;/a&gt;-infused weapon, in that it will deal bonus damage to skeletons and prevent them from reviving.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;"}
