{"id": "150146", "revid": "51254358", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=150146", "title": "Blindfold Mask", "text": "The Blindfold Mask (\u76ee\u96a0\u3057\u306e\u4eee\u9762) is a piece in \"\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Witch%20Set%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Black Witch Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nFound in &lt;a href=\"The%20Ringed%20City%20%28location%29\"&gt;The Ringed City&lt;/a&gt;. Guaranteed drop from the &lt;a href=\"Moaning%20Knight\"&gt;Moaning Knight&lt;/a&gt; within the &lt;a href=\"The%20Ringed%20City%20%28location%29%23Bonfires\"&gt;Shared Grave&lt;/a&gt; area.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Blindfold Mask is essentially the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; counterpart to the &lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20Dusk%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Crown of Dusk&lt;/a&gt;. Wearing the mask boosts the damage dealt by Dark spells by an amount between 10-12%, falling off the greater base damage the spell deals. This is not limited to Dark &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Sorceries&lt;/a&gt; like &lt;a href=\"Great%20Deep%20Soul\"&gt;Great Deep Soul&lt;/a&gt;, but also includes Dark &lt;a href=\"Pyromancy%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Pyromancies&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Miracles&lt;/a&gt; such as &lt;a href=\"Black%20Flame%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Black Flame&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dorhys%27%20Gnawing\"&gt;Dorhys' Gnawing&lt;/a&gt;, respectively. As well, any Dark damage inflicted by weaponry, including from buffs such as &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Blade\"&gt;Dark Blade&lt;/a&gt;, is increased by 5%.\nHowever, the trade-off for this is that the wearer incurs an increased 30% damage from Dark sources.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;"}
{"id": "59245", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=59245", "title": "Blinding Bolt", "text": "Blinding Bolt is a &lt;a href=\"Miracles%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\u00a0\nAvailability.\nReceived by trading the &lt;a href=\"Old%20King%20Soul\"&gt;Old King Soul&lt;/a&gt; and 10,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Straid%20of%20Olaphis\"&gt;Straid of Olaphis&lt;/a&gt;.\u00a0\nDescription.\nWhen used, a small ball of energy floats a few feet away from the caster. After a second, it starts shooting bolts of lighting in random directions. These bolts deal moderate damage, and light damage if it lands near the enemy. The ball of energy fires bolts in directions below the ball or to the side of the ball. It never fires upwards.\nIf the small ball of energy floats into a wall, ground, or ceiling, it evaporates, causing no damage. If the ball floats into an enemy, it deals moderate damage, but again evaporates.\nAttunement milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:"}
