{"id": "137152", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=137152", "title": "Blood Gem", "text": "Blood Gems are &lt;a href=\"Upgrade%20Materials%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;upgrade materials&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nUsage.\nThe player must obtain the &lt;a href=\"Profaned%20Coal\"&gt;Profaned Coal&lt;/a&gt; and give it to &lt;a href=\"Andre%20of%20Astora\"&gt;Andre of Astora&lt;/a&gt; to allow &lt;a href=\"Infusion%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;infusion&lt;/a&gt; of this gem into a &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt;.\nUse the Blood Gem to &lt;a href=\"Infusion%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;infuse&lt;/a&gt; a weapon with the &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; effect. The infusion will reduce base &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scaling%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt;, while adding or increasing Bleed &lt;a href=\"buildup\"&gt;buildup&lt;/a&gt;, which scales with &lt;a href=\"Luck\"&gt;Luck&lt;/a&gt;."}
